text: Novy () is a rural locality (a selo) in Beketovsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 313 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Yermekeyevo, 10 km from Beketovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Novy, Yermekeyevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
